sub_title: Director and Senior Teacher at Asfaloth BV
summary:
Asfaloth:
Writing and teaching Jungian psychology, Mythology, Tarot, Astrology, I Ching. Developing a digital learning environment (LMS) for astrology at bachelor-level.
Researching future tendencies using astrology; researching the astrology of world affairs, financial and economic developments and Zeitgeist.
Lecturing both national and international.
Advisor of Dasym Investment Strategies.

Symbolon publishing company:
Co-editor of journal MANTRA and the astrological journal Symbolon. 
Having written 36 books and many articles.
